HREF="http://www.pathfinder.com/@@GK2PJOGhBQEAQORA/vg/Welcome/welcome.html"><FONT
SIZE=4><B>The Virtual Garden</B></FONT></A> intends to be the most
comprehensive collection of consumer information on gardening available
online. It consists of a panoply of features derived from several Time
Inc. magazines and book publishers as well as contributions from the
world's leading public gardens and arboreta, professional botanists,
horticulturists and landscape architects, plant societies and gardening
experts.


<P><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.gardenweb.com/"><FONT SIZE=4><IMG SRC="garweb.GIF"
