<BLINK><H1>Professor Sir Harry Kroto Wins Nobel Prize </H1></BLINK>
<FONT SIZE="5">
It is announced today 9th October 1996 that the Nobel Prize for Chemistry has been awarded jointly to <A HREF="/faculty/hwk">
Professor Sir Harry Kroto </A>(Sussex), Professor Robert S. Curl and Professor Richard E. Smalley of 
Rice University, Houston.
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.nobel.se/announcement-96/chemistry96.html">Full details here.</A>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.almaz.com/nobel/Chemistry.html">Other Winners of the Nobel Prize for Chemistry.</A>
