<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000">
<CENTER>

<IMG SRC="/images/cpes.gif">   
<H3>Polymer Research</H3>
</CENTER>
<HR>
<A HREF="/faculty/spa/"><H3>Dr. S. P. Armes</H3></A>
<P>
Conducting polymers, sterically stabilised colloids. Polymer synthesis and characterisation.
<P>
<A HREF="/faculty/ncb/"><H3>Dr. N. C. Billingham</H3></A>
<P>
Synthesis of polymers for special applications. Degradation and stabilisation
of polymers. Cure reactions in thermosetting resins.
<P>
<A HREF="/sxres.html">Return to Research Index.
<IMG SRC="/images/mouse.gif" align="middle"></A>
