<UL>
<CENTER><P><B><I><FONT SIZE=+2>Hello, and welcome to Dr. Stephen Caddick's
Research Group Homepage.</FONT></I></B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="colorbar.gif" HEIGHT=3 WIDTH=600></P></CENTER>

<UL>
<P><B>At the moment, our group consists of a mixture of D.Phil. and Undergrad.
students carrying out very varied Chemistry research under Vern (our post-Doc.)
and Steve the Boss. You can find out what we all do by clicking on our
names, below. </B></P>
</UL>

<CENTER><P><B>(<I>Steve's Homepage will give you a general overview)</I>.</B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=+1>&nbsp;</FONT><B><FONT SIZE=+2>
<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/faculty/sc/">Dr. Stephen Caddick.</A></FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>&nbsp;
(Our Boss)&nbsp;</FONT></B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><B><FONT SIZE=+1><A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/vernhome.html">Dr
Vern Delisser</A> (Our Post-Doc)</FONT></B></P></CENTER>

<UL>
<CENTER><P><B><FONT SIZE=+1><A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/ssshome1.html">Sakthi
Shan</A>&nbsp; (Senior D.Phil. Student)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><B><FONT SIZE=+1><A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/safhome1.html">Safraz
Khan&nbsp;</A> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/vedhome1.html">Valerie
Doyle</A> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/kefhome1.html">Kirsty
Finch&nbsp;</A>&nbsp;(3rd. Year D.Phil Students)</FONT></B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><B><FONT SIZE=+1><A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/kjhome1.html">Kerry
Jenkins</A>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/clshome1.html">Craig
Shering</A>&nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/dmbhome1.html">Douglas
Barr</A>&nbsp;&nbsp;(2nd. Year D.Phil Students)&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><B><FONT SIZE=+1><A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/rwhome1.html">Rob
Weaving</A>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/sabhome1.html">Steve
Bromfield</A> &nbsp;(1st. Year D.Phil Students)</FONT></B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="colorbar.gif" HEIGHT=3 WIDTH=600></P></CENTER>

<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=+1>Our
Group&nbsp;is based in the School of Chemistry, Physics and Environmental
Science ('<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/">CPES</A>') at the <A HREF="http://www.susx.ac.uk/">University
of Sussex</A>, near Brighton in the U.K.</FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>Our Group is interested
in a number of different fields of Organic Chemistry;</FONT></P>

<UL>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Synthesis of Enediyne Natural Products and Analogues;
<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/vernhome.html">Vern</A>,
<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/ssshome1.html">Sakthi</A>,
<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/vedhome1.html">Val</A>,
<A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/safhome.html">Safraz</A>
&amp; <A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/dmbhome1.html">Doug</A>.</FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Stereochemistry of Organic compounds; <A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/kjhome1.html">Kerry</A></FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Microwave Assisted Organic Transformations; <A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/sabhome1.html">Steve</A></FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Novel Organic Methodology; <A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/kefhome1.html">Kirsty</A>,
<A HREF="http://www.cpes.sussex.ac.uk/resgrps/clshome1.html">Craig</A>
&amp; <A HREF="http://www.cpes.susx.ac.uk/resgrps/sjc/rwhome1.html">Rob</A>.</FONT></P>

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="colorbar.gif" HEIGHT=3 WIDTH=600></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><FONT SIZE=+1>Doug also maintains a page for post-Grad and post-Doc
chemists seeking jobs or research positions;</FONT></P></CENTER>

