<TITLE>Phil's Home Page</TITLE>
<SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JavaScript">
<!-- Beginning of JavaScript Applet -------------------

/* Copyright (C)1996 Web Integration Systems, Inc. DBA Websys, Inc.
   All Rights Reserved.
   This applet can be re-used or modified, if credit is given in 
   the source code.
   We will not be held responsible for any unwanted effects due to the 
   usage of this applet or any derivative.  No warrantees for usability 
   for any specific application are given or implied.
   Chris Skinner, January 30th, 1996.
   Hacked for CNNfn by RD, Jan. 31, 1996
*/
function scrollit_r2l(seed)
{
        var m1  = "Computer Workshop (CPES) The University of Sussex at Brighton ";
        var m2  = " ";
	var m3  = " ";
        var m4  = " ";
        var msg=m1+m2+m3+m4;
        var out = " ";
        var c   = 1;
        if (seed > 100) {
                seed--;
                var cmd="scrollit_r2l(" + seed + ")";
                timerTwo=window.setTimeout(cmd,100);
        }
        else if (seed <= 100 && seed > 0) {
                for (c=0 ; c < seed ; c++) {
                        out+=" ";
                }
                out+=msg;
                seed--;
                var cmd="scrollit_r2l(" + seed + ")";
                    window.status=out;
                timerTwo=window.setTimeout(cmd,100);
        }
        else if (seed <= 0) {
                if (-seed < msg.length) {
                        out+=msg.substring(-seed,msg.length);
                        seed--;
                        var cmd="scrollit_r2l(" + seed + ")";
                        window.status=out;
                        timerTwo=window.setTimeout(cmd,100);
                }
                else {
                        window.status=" ";
                        timerTwo=window.setTimeout("scrollit_r2l(100)",75);
                }
        }
}
// -- End of JavaScript code -------------- -->
</SCRIPT></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#CCFFFF" onLoad="timerONE=window.setTimeout('scrollit_r2l(100)',500);">
<P>
<P>
<TITLE>Phils Home Page</TITLE>
<P>
<P>
<P>
<img width=32 height=32 align="left" src="./images/juggler.gif">
<P>
<STRONG>Hello and a warm welcome to my home page.</STRONG>
<H1>Phil Chitty</H1>At work, I am responsible for the running of the Computer Workshop. I report directly to the Laboratory Resources
 Manager. I also look after the range of Apple Macintosh Computer's that we have in the school.
<P> Environmental monitoring is also another of my interests.
As a member of the Remote Imaging Group, I have set up a Weather
Satellite Receiving station in the Environmental Science room (MOLS
stage 2).<P> I have helped to set up a  3rd year U.G. project using a
special kite to lift atmospheric pollution monitoring equipment. The
observation of Ultra  Violet Radiation resulting from changes in the
Ozone layer is also being carried out.<P>
<UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.sussex.ac.uk"> University Information.</A><P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cpes.sussex.ac.uk"> School of Chemistry,Physics & Enviromental Science Home Page. </A>
</UL>
<HR>
