A Large kite picture taken at Weymouth 1995.</A><P><H3><A HREF="images/rain.gif"
>Here is a graph of Rainfall in the local area</A></H3><P><HR>
<H3>Interests:</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Today's Weather Satellite Pictures  <A HREF="http://www.sat.dundee.ac.uk/">www.sat.dundee.ac.uk</A></LI>
