 Kite Flyers</A> And to <A HREF="/services/sites.html"> Kite Sites Worldwide.</A>
<LI>Astronomy <A HREF="http://star-www.maps.sussex.ac.uk/index.html"> Astronomy at Sussex.</A>   And <A HREF="http://marvel.stsci.edu/pubinfo/Pictures.html">Hubble Space Telescope Images</A></LI>
</UL>
