   <title>Rob Weaving Homepage</title>
   <meta name="Author" content="Douglas M. Barr">
   <meta name="GENERATOR" content="Mozilla/3.0b4Gold (Win16)">
</head>
<body text="#FFFFFFFF" bgcolor="#000000" link="#FFFFFF00" vlink="#FFFFFFC0" alink="#FFFFFFC0" background="stars.gif">

<center><p><font SIZE=+4>Rob's Homepage</font> </p></center>

<center><p><img src="globe1.gif" height=60 width=56></p></center>

<center><p><img src="rob.jpg" border=0 height=291 width=203></p></center>

<p><font SIZE=+1>Hello, gis a job! I`m working on some aspects of iron
chemistry in synthesis. At present my project principally involves the
use of ferrates and Gif-Barton chemistry in oxidative transformations.
One long term aim of the work is to provide viable alternatives to toxic
tin reagants currently used extensively in radical based synthesis. In
the future I feel driven to make a large sum of money in order to help<a href="http://www.service.uit.no/mancity/homepage.html">
Man City</a> to European cup success;</font></p>

<center><p><a href="http://www.service.uit.no/mancity/homepage.html"><img src="mancity1.gif" border=2 height=163 width=163></a></p></center>

<center><p><img src="m0orf2qb.gif" border=0 height=9 width=720 align=abscenter></p></center>

