<center><p><b><font SIZE=+4>Safraz's Homepage</font></b> </p></center>

<center><p><img src="constrct.gif" border=0 height=28 width=465></p></center>

<center><p><img src="blumarbl.gif" border=0 height=8 width=581></p></center>

