   <td><H1><CITE><IMG SRC="../images/nzsmlogo.gif" height=66 width=240 ALIGN=top alt="New Zealand Science Monthly"></CITE></H1></td>
   <td width="16%"><A HREF="../changes.htm">Last updated</A><BR>
