<BODY BGCOLOR="#99DDFF"><H1 align="center">Welcome to Ros's Home Page</H1>
<HR align="center">

<IMG src="images/roz1.jpg" alt="Photo of Ros" height="300" width="214" hspace="7" ALIGN=Left>
<P>This is an introduction to Ros Davis, my background, interests and abilities, and some links to some of the organisations I am involved with. I hope you enjoy it.</P>

