<H2> <BR clear=left><A name="Ros">Ros</A></H2>
<P><BIG>Totem Animal:</BIG><BR>Cat</P>
<P><BIG>Star Sign:</BIG><BR>What day is it?</P>
<P><BIG>Loves:</BIG><BR>Making things<BR>Reading anything I can get my hands on<BR>Music<BR>Dressing up in funny clothes and <A HREF="madelein.htm">playing at living in C15th Europe</A></P>
<P><BIG>Loathes:</BIG><BR>Politiking<BR>Neighbours who play loud music of a type I don't personally enjoy<BR>Getting up in the morning when it's dark</P>
 <P><BIG>Fondest wishes:</BIG><BR>To join the idle rich<BR>To buy my mountain hideaway</P>

<H3>What I do with my time:</H3>

<P>Have <EM>you</EM> ever eaten a 500-year-old meal, or tried to persuade an eleven-year-old to wear tights? Plus there is family, work, <A href="stmikes.htm">Church</A>, friends, and sometimes even some time to just blob in front of the TV and watch Star Trek reruns!</P>

