</TABLE>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Welcome to WebCentre...<BR>
<SMALL>...Where Quality is more than Screen Deep</SMALL>
</H1>

<TABLE width="100%">
<TR align=left><TH width="33%">Contents</TH><TH width="33%">Products</TH><TH>Features</TH></TR>
<TR valign=top>
<TD><A HREF= "#About">About WebCentre</A></TD>
<TD><A href="webview.htm">SPIS Webview Offline Browser</A></TD>
<TD><A HREF= "../climb.htm">Climbing Out On The Web</A> (our Web Site Primer)</TD>
</TR>
<TR valign=top>
<TD><A HREF= "#Sites We Made">Sites We Made</A></TD>
<TD><A href="webwatch.htm">SPIS Webwatch Site Monitor</A></TD>
<TD><A HREF= "../webpacks.htm">Our Web Site packages</A> -- pick the kind of site that's best for you</TD>
</TR>
<TR valign=top>
<TD><A HREF="#Sites We Like">Sites We Like</A></TD>
