<table width="100%">
<tr>
  <td ALIGN=CENTER><H1>Welcome to SPIS WebWatch!</H1>
   <P><I>A Web Site Monitor for<BR>WinNT and Win95</I><P>
    <!--Webber_Auto_StampDNR-->Last Updated: <!--DS-->02-10-96<!---->
