TCompress Component Set V2.5</H1>
<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>File and Database Compression Components for Delphi 1.0 and 2.0</H3>
     <H4 ALIGN=CENTER>Peter Hyde, South Pacific Information Services Ltd</H4>
<H4 Align=Center> <!--Webber_Auto_StampDNR-->Last Updated: <!--DS-->November 10 1996<!----></H4>
