<HR>
<H2><A Name="Order">Ordering terms and information:</A></H2>
<P>To order from South Sea Books, simply mark the check-boxes for the titles you want, then complete the ordering information at the end of the section. Within a day, we'll send you an order confirmation and invoice including postage costs and insurance.
<UL>
<LI>Prices stated are in US dollars and do <I>not</I> include postage.</LI>
<LI>Payment may also be made by cheque to the equivalent value in $NZ, sterling or $A, drawn on a bank in your country.</LI>
<LI>For orders over $US60, payment may be made using Visa or Mastercard.</LI>
<LI>First-time orders require pre-payment on our invoice before books are shipped.</LI>
<LI>All books are octavo size, cloth bound, 1st edition, unless otherwise stated.</LI>
<LI>Major faults are described but, for lower priced books, faults such as inscriptions on front endpapers or pencil notations etc. are not. Books found with uncatalogued faults may be returned within 14 days and a refund will be given.</LI>
</UL>
<P><I>For more information, contact:</I><BR>
Glenn Haszard<BR>
South Sea Books<BR>
