   <TD><A HREF="#You">You and the Web</A><BR>...the benefits of your own site</TD>
   <TD><A HREF="#Promotion">Web Site Promotion</A></TD>
   <TD><A HREF="#Service">NZ Web Service Providers</A></TD>
   </TR>
