<A NAME="ElectronicPublishing"></A><H2>Electronic Publishing</H2>

<P><BIG><STRONG>SPIS</STRONG></BIG> doesn't just stand for South Pacific Information Services, it also stands for the sort of work we do:

<TABLE Width="85%">
<TR>
   <TD Width="15%"><STRONG>Sophisticated</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We know that you want your electronic material to be a cut above the rest, and we can ensure the level of
           sophistication you want.</TD>
   </TR>
<TR>
   <TD><STRONG>Practical</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We're not just ideas people, we're also intensely practical -- our ideas work.</TD>
   </TR>
<TR>
   <TD><STRONG>Imaginative</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We think of imaginative ways of using new media  -- take a look at <A HREF="/spis/wop.htm"><CITE>
           The Weekly O'Press</CITE></A> or <A HREF="/spis/climb.htm"><CITE>Climbing Out on the Web.</CITE></A></TD>
   </TR>
<TR>
   <TD><STRONG>Skillful</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We've got the skills to meet your demands -- use them.</TD>
   </TR>
</TABLE>

<P>Everyone's excited about electronic publishing, whether on the Web or off-line, but not a lot of people have the information or the ability to use this new media to its fullest potential. We've got the skills and knowledge to help you make the most of your electronic publishing opportunities.

<P>If you want to use electronic access as part of your national and international marketing strategy, electronic marketing offers a whole new field of opportunity. We provide services that range from basic information or promotional packages in electronic form through to the production of electronic catalogues that will keep your staff and your customers up to date with what you have to offer.
 
<A NAME="WebPage"></A><H3>Web site design and maintenance</H3>

<P>Top Web sites get thousands of visits each day and they achieve that popularity for very good reasons -- they're well designed, interesting, interactive. We can help you design your Web site so people will want to visit it, learning about your organisation and its activities -- just as they do with our popular Web site primer <A HREF="/spis/climb.htm"><CITE>Climbing Out on the Web.</CITE></A>

<P>Web pages are often dynamic -- generated from product or information databases as required. We have the design skills and tools to automatically deliver information on demand.

<P>Design is an important starting point but if a Web page goes "stale", people notice. On-going maintenance is important, particularly when you Web page is acting as your electronic front door.

<P>We can take the drudgery of Web page maintenance out of your hands by providing regular re-designs and updates at designated intervals, or through daily monitoring and analysis of how your page is received in the competitive electronic scene.

<P>In addition to <A HREF="/spis/climb.htm"><CITE>Climbing Out on the Web,</CITE></A> we have a selection of sample <A HREF="webpacks.htm#All">Web site designs</A> with indicative pricing, including:</P>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="webpacks.htm#Hello">Hello World</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="webpacks.htm#Presence">Presence Package</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="webpacks.htm#Communication">Communication Package</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="webpacks.htm#Commerce">Commerce Package</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="webpacks.htm#Other">Additional Services</A></LI>
</UL>

<P><A href="http://www.synet.net/hwg/"><IMG src="images/guild.gif" alt="Member of HTML Writers' Guild"></A>

<A NAME="Computer"></A><H3>Computer-based documentation</H3>

<P>How often have you had to hunt for a manual, only to find that it's well out of date as far as your system is concerned? On-line documentation offers an effective way of ensuring that your documentation is up-to-date and accessible to everyone.

<P>We can organise disk, network or CD-based documentation using standard tools such as Adobe Acrobat&reg; or HTML, with access systems designed to make it easy to read and use on screen. You can update and distribute your documentation at will, allowing everyone to benefit.

<A NAME="OnlineHelp"></A><H3>On-line help and support systems</H3>

<P>Software is only as good as the information used to run it and support it. We can design effective Windows-based help systems that can solve many of the bottlenecks experienced as people struggle to use new packages.

<P>Not only that, but we can provide on-line support sites with dial-in or Net access to new files, support information and product releases.

<P>Use our services to get your users off to a good start, and keep them happy when they start to extend themselves!

<HR>

<A NAME="SoftwareEngineering"></A>

<H2>Software Engineering</H2>

<P><BIG><STRONG>SPIS</STRONG></BIG> doesn't just stand for South Pacific Information Services, it also stands for the kind of software we produce:

<TABLE Width="85%">
<TR>
   <TD Width="15%"><STRONG>Sound</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We pride ourselves on producing sound software that meets the specifications on time.</TD>
   </TR>
<TR>
   <TD><STRONG>Polished</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We don't stop at writing good code, but make sure that our software is well polished, reliable and fully
           documented.</TD>
   </TR>
<TR>
   <TD><STRONG>Innovative</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We're always keeping an eye out for innovative solutions, new approaches and the perfect programming
          language so we can produce the best possible product.</TD>
   </TR>
<TR>
   <TD><STRONG>Supported</STRONG></TD>
   <TD>We know that support is important, and we don't stint in providing whatever level of support is required.</TD>   </TR>
</TABLE>

<P>Our software engineering services are designed to supplement and enhance your resources. We offer a broad range of skills, from quality software development and technical support to full documentation production.

<P>Our international experience ranges from system software, such as word processors and database management systems, through to end-user applications, such as image processing, management, scientific and presentation systems. Visa International liked our innovative approach when it came to developing a comprehensive <A HREF="/spis/softserv.htm#MediaMonitor">media monitoring</A> system.

<A NAME="Programming"></A><H3>Programming: Delphi and Paradox</H3>

<P>We keep tabs on new developments in the software scene so we can offer the most appropriate and most effective software environments.

<P>Our primary development base is currently Windows and OS/2, using advanced system and database development software such as <A HREF="http://http://www.borland.com/">Borland</A> <A HREF="http://iconz.co.nz/commercial/Borland/Delphi/home.htm">Delphi,</A> C++ and Paradox for Windows.

<P>Our latest product is <A HREF="compress.htm">TCompress</A>, a file and database compression component for Delphi, which has attracted orders from as far afield as Sweden and Slovenia. <A HREF="/spis/softserv.htm#ElectronicPublishing">Electronic marketing</A> has helped its spread internationally.

<P>The research and skills we put together to make and document TCompress and <CITE>MediaMonitor</CITE> are at your disposal.

<A NAME="MediaMonitor"></A>

<H3><CITE>MediaMonitor</CITE> software</H3>

<P>Got a mountain of press clippings going yellow and mouldering in some filing cabinet for lack of use? Burn them! Instead, use <CITE>MediaMonitor</CITE>, an advanced Windows-based package to effectively automate the gathering, storage, retrieval and analysis of your press material.

<P><CITE>MediaMonitor</CITE> clients such as Visa International and Barclays Plc use it as an effective way of storing and analysing vast quantities of press clippings (including scanned images) collected by their PR agencies. Instead of the paper wars they had previously, they now have instant online access and sophisticated analysis and trend-tracking.

<P>This gives them -- and can give you -- valuable and timely information on market, social, technology and regulatory trends, to keep a step ahead of the bunch.

<A NAME="RelatedServices"></A><H3>Related Services</H3>

<H4>Consultancy and training</H4>

<P>Our international experience and extensive <A HREF="/spis/pin.htm">information network</A> permit us to offer a range of consulting and training services including:

<UL>
<LI>Market research and strategic advice</LI>
<LI><EM>Internationalisation</EM> of software packages</LI>
<LI>Tracking technology trends and technical information</LI>
