<LI>Alpha- and beta-testing of completed systems</LI>
</UL>

<H4>Documentation</H4>

<P>Our technical knowledge, excellent communications skills and <A HREF="/spis/editserv.htm">publishing technology</A> means that we're a real boon to people who want their documentation (of whatever variety) to reflect the professional standards and quality they've brought to their product.

<P>Successful companies recognise the need to have documentation that's effective and intelligible -- which is why companies like Panasonic come to us.

We offer:
<UL>
<LI>Design, writing and production of documentation for new products</LI>
<LI>Editing and revision of existing documentation</LI>
<LI>Adaptation or translation for overseas markets</LI>
<LI>Improvement of client documentation procedures</LI>
<LI>And of course if you want the documentation <A HREF="/spis/softserv.htm#OnlineHelp">online,</A> we can do that too
</UL>


