<P><A HREF="/spis/images/stereosa.gif"><IMG SRC="/spis/images/s_stereo.gif" ALT=[Sample] ALIGN=center></A> (41K)

<P>Autostereograms are often produced to decorate postcards or greetings cards.  You can have your corporate or personal logo appear out of a background of your choice. We can create just the image (either on disk, or as a colour laser-printed masterpiece), or we can design and print the cards for you.

<P>Your cards, posters and tee-shirts can also showcase specially-commissioned <A HREF="/spis/people.htm#nick">Nick</A> cartoons, targeted at your activities or audience.

