<!-- Created by Peter Hyde,   (c) 1995   South Pacific Information Services Ltd       -->
<!-- If you want to contact us, phone +64-3-384-5137  fax: +64-3-384-5138              -->
<!-- email: nzsm@spis.co.nz    -->
