<A NAME="Fitz"></A><H1>Peter Fitzpatrick (Fitz)</H1>
<TABLE>
<TR>
  <TD VALIGN=TOP width="15%"><BIG>Totem Animal:</BIG><BR>Elephant</TD><TD width="20%"></TD>
 <TD VALIGN=TOP width="15%"><BIG>Star Sign:</BIG><BR>Emma Thompson<TD>
 <TD VALIGN=TOP width="20%"><BIG>Loves:</BIG><BR>Aikido<BR>Fresh clean drawing paper<BR><A HREF="http://www.lfbs.rwth-aachen.de/~markolf/Moto_Links.html">Powerful motorcycles</A><BR></TD>
 <TD VALIGN=TOP width="20%"><BIG>Loathes:</BIG><BR>Getting out of bed<BR>Silverbeet<BR><A HREF="http://www.greenpeace.org/~comms/rw/pkcant.html">Jacques Chirac</A></TD>
 <TD VALIGN=TOP width="30%"><BIG>Fondest wish:</BIG><BR>To become phenomenally wealthy and live a life of sybaritic luxury without ever having to work for it</TD>
