<H1><CITE><IMG SRC="../images/nzsmlogo.gif" height=66 width=240 ALIGN=top alt="NZ Science Monthly "></CITE> NZ and International Science Links</H1>

<H2>New Zealand</H2>

<A href="http://www.sci.waikato.ac.nz/smcluster/home.html"><BIG>Strange Matter</BIG></A><BR>
A home for Nick's cartoons!

<H3>Crown Research Institutes</H3>
<ul>
   <li><a href="http://www.agresearch.cri.nz/">AgResearch</a> (NZ Pastoral Agriculture Research Institute)<BR>
      Pastoral agriculture - from basic reasearch to processing and marketing.
   <li><A HREF="http://www.crop.cri.nz/">Crop &amp; Food Research</A><BR>
      Research concerning the production and processing of arable crops, vegetables, glasshouse crops, flowers, seafood...
   <li><a href="http://www.gns.cri.nz/">GNS</a> (Institute of Geological &amp; Nuclear Sciences)<BR>
      Fundamental research in geosciences, geohazard assessment, energy and mineral resources; application of nuclear science.
   <LI><A HREF = "http://www.hort.cri.nz/">Hort+Research</A> (Horticulture and Food Research Institute of NZ)<BR>
      Horticultural research, especially fresh fruit exports and crop processing.
   <li><a href="http://www.irl.cri.nz/">Industrial Research Ltd</a><BR>
      Research and technology to aid the development of new products, processes and services.</li>
   <li><a href="http://www.landcare.cri.nz/">Manaaki Whenua - Landcare Research</a><BR>
      Science concerning land, landscapes, soil, plants and animals and their interrelationships.</li>
   <li><a href="http://www.niwa.cri.nz/">NIWA</A> (National Institute of Water &amp; Atmospheric Research)<BR>
      Providing a scientific basis for the sustainable management of atmospheric, freshwater and marine systems.
</ul>

<H3>Universities</H3>
