<H2>Why did we do this?</H2>

<P>You choose:
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="/spis/pin.htm#spis">Our</A> main philanthropic philosophy is the belief that people should be informed and think hard about important issues in order to function as effective citizens</LI>
<LI>The issues we cover raise interesting and important points about our society that need broader discussion</LI>
<LI>Everyone deserves their 15 minutes of fame</LI>
<LI>We get a chance to show off our <A HREF="/spis/softserv.htm#WebPage">Web design skills</A> with some serious and not-so-serious material</LI>
<LI>We wanted to see if we could produce an interesting set of pages in <STRONG>one day flat</STRONG></LI>
<LI><A HREF="/spis/people.htm#Peter">Peter</A> couldn't get to sleep early one Saturday morning</LI>
<LI>All of the above</LI>
</UL>

