<tr>
<TD COLSPAN=3><A HREF="climwhat.htm">What is the Web, you and the Web, site design</A></TD><TD COLSPAN=2><A HREF="climsite.htm">Example sites, development resources, service providers</A></TD>
</tr>
<tr>
   <td><IMG SRC="images/letters.gif" alt=""><A HREF="mailto:climb@spis.co.nz">Mail us</A></td>
